summary: This is an internal FBI email chain from September 10, 2019, regarding coordination for proffers and interviews in the West Palm Beach area as part of the ongoing Epstein investigation. It indicates investigative activity in that region.

events.title: FBI Coordination for WPB Interviews
events.description: FBI personnel from New York notify FBI personnel in another office (likely West Palm Beach) that they will be conducting proffers and interviews in their Area of Responsibility (AOR) for the Epstein investigation.

locations: West Palm Beach (WPB) - Referenced as the Area of Responsibility (AOR) where proffers and interviews are to be conducted.
keyFacts: The FBI was actively conducting proffers and interviews in the Epstein investigation as of September 2019.
The investigative activity involved coordination between different FBI field offices, specifically referencing the West Palm Beach (WPB) area.
The communication is a routine internal coordination email, indicating ongoing investigative steps.
